Package: ggerror
Title: Extended Error Geoms for 'ggplot2'
Version: 0.3.0
Authors@R:
    person("Yann", "Cohen", , "yannco5@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0009-0509-3609"))
Description: Extends the 'ggplot2' range geoms with an error-first API.
    geom_error() accepts an 'error' aesthetic, or 'error_neg' and
    'error_pos' for asymmetric cases, infers orientation from the data,
    computes bounds, and dispatches to geom_errorbar(),
    geom_linerange(), geom_crossbar(), or geom_pointrange().
    Also supports fixed per-side styling for asymmetric or one-sided
    error bars.
